se.miun.itm.input.model.param

Class InPUTConstructor

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.model.param.InPUTConstructor

  • public class InPUTConstructor
extends java.lang.Object
    An internal representation of a constructor, which is a wrapper of the reflect.constructor class, including the information from the InPUT mapping descriptors. It keeps track of its dependencies, and how to get hold of the values that it requires for correct instantiation.
    Author:
    Felix Dobslaw
